{"tid":2004180,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"投票贏咗可能冇用，但係至少人哋用都冇得用","createTime":"2020-05-06T09:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T13:45:37.000Z","uid":46688,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd363d6ce02936fdfe7246cb72328330d07664f","tid":2004180,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"有人認為議會抗爭其實對我哋冇乜用，但係大家可以再諗深一層，我哋冇用但係班支共狗有用，如果贏咗我哋至少可以令到佢哋少咗一樣工具，所以除咗立法會區議會，有得攞嘅都攞咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，樓長層長甚至係學生會都攞晒佢，唔可以畀支共狗攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（屋苑法團或者委員會好重要，可以影響區議員做嘢）<br />\n<br />\n有人會問，屌唔係要攬炒嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣做其實正正係可以加速攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇吓中西區嗰單嘢支共做到幾核突，支共政權透過唔到投票贏，就會用好核突嘅方法去穩固自己嘅政權繼續壓迫我哋。<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家可以把握自己嘅投票機會或者參選機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，攞咗先好過冇攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆不分化不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0e64031d56dd76b6f71d85d7a7ea4153d58d330b","tid":2004180,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:23:53.000Z","msg":"贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf402a549735311bdf9c5633275e980189895ff1","tid":2004180,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a1ca276f1fb442d6426fa4911959093dd05edf","tid":2004180,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693a9444cd3af7a67ee6d9780200890dfd3ec166","tid":2004180,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c66e23f12b78e38ba83f52200952a